|-
| 罐鼎 || 器身似敛口束颈罐，圜底 || [[File:Ding_(cooking_vessel),_China,_Shang_dynasty,_1300-1046_BC,_bronze_-_Royal_Ontario_Museum_-_DSC03993.JPG|150px]] || 
|-
| 鬲鼎 || 器腹作袋足形，似[[鬲|鬲]]，但实足，有双耳 || [[File:Li_Ding_with_Eye_and_Thunder_Veins.jpg|150px]] || 
